---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container about-inner">
    <div class="about-media">
      <span class="logo-badge about-badge">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="Ozark Fulfillment logo" width="240" height="240" />
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">About Ozark Fulfillment</h2>
      <p>
        Ozark Fulfillment is an owner-operated third-party logistics (3PL) provider helping
        e-commerce brands scale across every channel they sell on. From our 65,000 sq ft
        warehouse in Houston, Missouri, we handle Amazon FBA prep, Walmart WFS prep,
        direct-to-consumer fulfillment, and B2B/wholesale distribution — all under one roof.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our services include FNSKU labeling, polybagging, bundling, carton forwarding, and
        value-added work like kitting and custom packaging, backed by flexible storage that
        includes 9,000 sq ft of climate-controlled space. Our central-US location puts your
        inventory within favorable shipping zones to most of the country, and our
        owner-operated model means you get direct account management — not a ticket queue.
      </p>
      <a href="#quote" class="btn btn-primary">Work With Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.2fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .about-badge {
    width: min(240px, 60vw);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: block;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .about-copy p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }

  .about-copy .btn {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-badge {
      width: min(180px, 45vw);
    }
  }
</style>
